---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About Me"
	description="jiechen — AI / Cloud / DevOps Engineer building small, useful developer tools."
	pubDate={new Date('August 08 2021')}
	heroImage="/blog-placeholder-about.jpg"
>
	<p>
		Hi, I'm <strong>jiechen</strong> (GitHub <a href="https://github.com/bbfans">@bbfans</a>), an
		<strong>AI / Cloud / DevOps Engineer</strong>. This site is where I keep notes on the tools
		I'm building, the systems I'm learning from, and the small experiments that make my workflow
		better.
	</p>

	<p>
		My current work sits around AI agent workflows, backend systems, FastAPI, Playwright
		automation, and practical TypeScript/Python tooling. I care about systems that are easy to
		deploy, easy to inspect, and useful enough to run every day.
	</p>

	<p>
		I use <a href="https://bbfans.github.io">bbfans.github.io</a> as a public workbench: part
		project index, part changelog, part technical journal. The writing here is intentionally
		close to the work, with rough edges removed only when they get in the way.
	</p>

	<p>
		If you want the shortest version: I like making developer tools that stay small, ship fast,
		and explain themselves in code.
	</p>
</Layout>
